An apple walks into a bar and sees a beautiful pear. The apple buys the pear a drink and they begin talking to each other. The pear and the Apple have a lot in common. They talk about their favorite movies. The apple says its alltime favourite movie is the 2012 hit film Foodfight! starring Charlie Sheen and Hilary Duff. The pear extatically claims that's its favourite movie too. The apple invites the pear back to his place to watch it together. Several months later the pear is now living with the apple rent free. One day the apple comes home from work to find the pear sleeping with a grapefruit! The apple, torn with grief, feeds itself to a horse.
